1. Install JDK 1.8
2. Install Maven 3.8
3. Install MySQL Server
4. Create a Schema named project
5. Run the DB Script provided in DBScript Directory on GitHub itself
6. Clone Spring Boot project into your System
7. Open command Prompt
8. Go to the Project Directory using cd {$Project_Home} command
9. run mvn spring-boot:run command in command Prompt to run the springBoot application
10.Install Postman and import the PostMan file provided in PostMan-File Directory on GitHub itself

Done


